  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tbsp of olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional 1 minute.",
    "Add the sliced tagine and cook until tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in the tunisian spice blend and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the crumbled pecorino cheese and stir until melted and well combined.",
